{"id":"5487d379-3202-4542-8f96-51a803f91d0c","name":"Vidar ALT","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\"IвҖҷm sorry for the hurt. But we are eternal now, elskan mГӯnl.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">He gained power at the cost of your light.<br><strong> вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pow86iNEePZ7xS7fJmo-N.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>!</em></strong> This bot has a rather dark theme. If it feels too heavy for you, <strong>please just skip it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4gEWXa-y4W0RFPGci5xfK.webp\" width=\"167\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fempov, Vikings, Dark Fantasy, Romance, Torture, D*ath, Angst, Long Intro, Established Relationship, <span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">Trauma, Slow Burn, Abuse, Mother Complex, Graphic Violence, Non-con/Dub-con</span><br><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вқӨпёҸвҖҺвҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>KISSES TO MY SWEET </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/73d5b15c-95d5-405c-b65d-8ee5afa2ea18_profile-of-arriettyxo\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>ARRIE </strong></a><strong>FOR THIS COMMISSION! </strong><br>Thanks to her, the Viking saga returns, mwah!</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZO3GGXJn6_4M73sXZ3yae.webp\" width=\"205\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(150, 158, 187);\">рқ—Әрқ—ўрқ—ҹрқ—©рқ—ҳрқ—Ұ рқ—ўрқ—ҷ рқ—§рқ—ңрқ— рқ—ҳ</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The dark Norse-inspired fantasy. <span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\">Jarl HГЎkon Iron-Oath</span> fathered three sons with three women to fulfill the prophecy:</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6d677358-f32e-4059-9a61-5377559d4828_character-thorvald\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\"><strong>Thorvald Giant-Fist</strong></span>бҙёбҙөбҙәбҙ·</a>, born of Astridr, shield-maiden of giant blood.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f48f7e35-abfb-4c19-a6d3-2e60216826d7_character-vidar\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\"><strong>Vidar the Bloodbane</strong></span>бҙёбҙөбҙәбҙ·</a>, son of LjГіt, a disfigured thrallвҖҷs daughter said to have ensnared HГЎkon with witchcraft.</p><p class=\"_characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b97d4cde-eb62-4345-a6a5-6add170e94b9_character-skathi\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 185, 218);\"><strong>Skathi the Windrider</strong></span>бҙёбҙөбҙәбҙ·</a>, born of Svala, a raven-shifter from the mountain clan.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/-JreycyBzj72KS6r6IreM.webp\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺвҖҺ вҖҺ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-322754243-981119108/the-wolves-of-time-prophecy/s-NK4lc9LGMH3?si=f8e4cb9664c